    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission are solid, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the clear coat. The interior is intact but shows typical wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It has been maintained enough to stay dependable, though it will eventually need some suspension work and a fresh set of tires. It\u2019s an honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 19500.0,
