    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a dedicated project car. The engine requires significant work to be roadworthy, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows heavy wear including several dents and rusted panels, while the interior has significant tearing and requires a complete detail. It is priced to reflect these necessary repairs and is sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 5500.0,
